	   change XVel by 1
	   if x position > 215
	   set x t 215
	   if key left arrow pressed?
	   change XVel by -1
	   if x position < -215
	   set x to - 215
	   set XVel to XVel * 0.8
	   set Coodernada_X_Posicao to x position
	   change x by Xvel
